<h1>Sports and Art Winter Camp</h1>

<p>Our 2018 Winter Camp is fast approaching and we are looking forward to taking part in a range of sports and art activities for all!</p>
<p>We are excited to see some familiar faces and also to meet some new friends. Please join us!</p>

<h3>Dates:</h3>
<ul class="list-unstyled">
  <li>December 17th to 21st</li>
  <li>Hours: 9:00am - 3:30pm</li>
</ul>

<h3>Ages:</h3>
<ul class="list-unstyled">
  <li>5 - 11 years old</li>
</ul>

<h3>Costs:</h3>
<ul class="list-unstyled">
  <li>1 day: 12,000円</li>
  <li>Full Week: 50,000円</li>
</ul>

